cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with state estimation in a control setting, which is a common topic in the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category. The use of the Kalman filter and other statistical methods suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The application of the results to demand dispatch for power grids suggests that the paper may also belong to the networking and internet architecture (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the use of mean field control and population models suggests that the paper may also belong to the learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
